        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 12 at 11:47PM EDT by NWS Albany NY</headline>
        <description>Patchy freezing drizzle may occur in some spots tonigt, mainly at
elevations greater than 1000 feet where temperatures are around
freezing. Untreated surfaces could become icy in these areas.
Motorists and pedestrians are urged to use caution if out and
about in the Berkshires this evening.
